# hooks/ directory
#
# Put your deterministic gate scripts here (block-default-branch, tests-before-push,
# auto-format, etc.) and wire them in hooks/hooks.json:
#
#   hooks/hooks.json   ← event → matcher → command wiring
#   hooks/*.sh         ← the scripts, referenced as "${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}"/hooks/<name>.sh
#
# All scripts must be executable (chmod +x) and fail OPEN: if a tool is missing,
# do not break the workflow.
#
# Delete this file when you add your first real hook, or remove the whole folder if
# the plugin needs no hooks.
